profile:
Today with over 15 years of experience  along side my father with over 45 years as a Blacksmith Master we work together to create new modern and contemporary designs. 

With our old fashioned techniques and modern day equipment the designs we can create are endless. We work with only the highest quality material and products which have built our reputation for reliable long lasting works of art. Wrought Iron Design Ltd works with Mild Steel, Aluminum, Stainless Steel and Copper.
